  "title": "Executive, Telemarketing",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in executing telemarketing campaigns and daily outreach activities</li>\n  <li>Support the Business Development team in identifying potential leads and customer segments</li>\n  <li>Make outbound calls and follow up with customers to promote services and gather</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with other departments for promotions, events, and customer service efforts</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate records of customer interactions and campaign results, and escalate feedback as required to improve service and campaign effectiveness</li>\n  <li>Ensure all telemarketing activities follow regulatory and company policies and compliance standards at all times</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Meet the relevant Regulatory Authority's statutory requirement of minimum 21 years of age</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in customer service roles or similar industry</li>\n  <li>Willing to work rotating shifts, including weekends and public holidays</li>\n</ul>",
